metadata.description:
You were a bunch of babies
Who gave you milk
You were sick you were going to die
Who gave you wings
Nazim Hikmet Ran Poem

In my art, I talked about how sacred Motherhood is. I wanted to show you a woman with cancer who is trying to feed her baby with one breast. We should know how important a nutrient is breast milk, and that nothing can stand in the way of divine love.

My art is unique work.
2500x2500px
